reviews.review:
Look: Star Wars is just another IP. It's a means to make money and sell toys--I've made my peace with that. The art design is great. The scenes are all composed well. But it's basically a Fast & Furious movie now. Death is not only completely meaningless in Star Wars--I'm now questioning why Luke doesn't just defeat everyone as a Force Ghost, because he's shown to be perfectly capable of affecting the world and using the force as if he were alive. Rey and Kilo are capable of fully omniscient, except for the times the script says they're not. Also, there may be regular ghosts in Star Wars now. I say "may" because it's unclear. 
Whatever. Star Wars is dumb.

This is the year of disappointing finales indeed, yay (?) I went into the cinema with zero expectations, I still came out disappointed. Never had I wanted to leave the cinema as badly as when I watched this absolute garbage of a show.

Plot: 1/10
Dialogue: 1/10
Acting: 1/10
Light saber fights: 1/10
Space battles: 1/10

Everything about this pathetic attempt of a movie was terrible. Just total, absolute, garbage. There are b-grade movies and animes that you only watch with drunk friends, and those were better than this.

Please. Let this die already.
I loved it. Fixed some issues from Last Jedi. Great way to end a 42 year journey. It's the ending we needed.
The movie is awesome, will see it again many more times!

It did it's best to fix everything, that ' The Last Jedi' broke and it was a good conclusion to the sequel trilogy, but not to the whole Skywalker saga, let's just say, that 'The Return of The Jedi' did the job for it. Also, I loved, that it had a lot of fans service. All in all great Star Wars movie, but can't compare it to the original ones.

Excellent way to close out the last trilogy! Fantastic in every aspect from the characters to the action down to the legacy this series had been known for.
This movie corrects many mistakes made in the last 2 movies in the Skywalker saga.   Nostalgic feeling was high.  Excellent closure to all the beloved characters from the original trilogy.

Main cast is great but this movie is really, really bad.
Easily bottom 3 in the saga, strong contender for worst plot.
Un buen cierre contemplando todos los errores que se tuvieron que reparar, no fue lo  mejor pero se supo hacer lo que tenian en las manos
